": false, "score": 13, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "censored", "id": 8726826, "raw_content": "", "author": "BlackCrimesMatter", "created": 1783972118222, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Cowpill", "is_video": true, "video_link": "https://cdn.videy.co/nx3TICYK1.mp4", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "cdn.videy.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://cdn.videy.co/nx3TICYK1.mp4", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Animals almost murder a white child while trying to kill her mother. What if this was your daughter? ", "last_comment_created": 1783974951063, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 13, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "\ud83d\udd25\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0BURN,\u00a0\u00a0LOOT,\u00a0\u00a0MURDER\u00a0\u00a0\ud83d\udd25", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqgMiO3", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 19, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8726643, "raw_content": "Trump was being shot at and thought he may die. The last words he wanted to tell us were \u201cfight.\u201d\n\nMany of you retards took that to mean we should start infighting with republicans, celebrating the death of republicans, and dividing MAGA as much as possible.\n\nThe Trump assassination attempt and Kirk assassination attempt should have united the entire right. It doesn\u2019t matter if you\u2019re a Lolbertarian, a MAGA populist, or an old blood neocon. We all have far more in common with each other than we do when the leftist commies trying to destroy America.\n\nAll it took to get many of you to turn on Trump was a little bit of low IQ propaganda. Some bullshit catering to your retardation about a global pedophile ring run by Israel that Trump was protecting, because reasons. This is the opposite of the \u201cfighting\u201d that Trump was advocating.\n\nLindsay Graham, despite his flaws, understood how to play as a team. He was once asked, \u201cwhy are you campaigning for Blake Masters when he has called you a bloodthirsty neocon for supporting the Ukraine war?\u201d\n\nHis response was, \u201clook, Masters is wrong about Ukraine, but he\u2019s a Republican and I will always fight to save the senate from Democrats.\u201d\n\nThis is the type of maturity and focus our movement needs to ever make an impact. Infighting because a Republican disagrees with you on 5% of issues is retarded. We all agree Islamists are the enemy and the left is the enemy. We mostly just have different opinions on how and when we should use our military. \n\nI don\u2019t support war with Russia, but these aren\u2019t disagreements worth burning the house down over. Either get on the MAGA train or get the fuck off. Trump is the leader, he supports war with Iran, as he has since the 1980s. He supports Ukraine to some mild extent.  If this is a dealbreaker for you, fine. Fuck off. \n\nIf you still support Trump even though you disagree sometimes, that is fine. What is not acceptable is accusing the President of being an \u201cIsraeli shill.\u201d What is not acceptable is trying to sabotage the GOP in elections because of sloppy \u201cIsrael\u201d propaganda, like Nick Fuentes. You want to make MAGA something it never stood for and pretend you are \u201creal MAGA\u201d. Fuck off and find a new movement, you brigading faggot.\n\nThe GOP is the only way to stop the left. Even if you hated Graham, you can learn something from his example of being a team player. Either follow our leader or fuck off. Uniting requires excising cancerous dividers from the movement who advocate we abandon Trump (or anyone in the GOP) because of one issue.\n\nUnite the right. Fight the left. ", "author": "STFUmuslimCUCKS", "created": 1783964457883, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "LandoNorris", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "When Trump said \u201cfight, fight, fight\u201d he wasn\u2019t talking about fighting Republicans.", "last_comment_created": 1783969940071, "content": "<p>Trump was being shot at and thought he may die. The last words he wanted to tell us were \u201cfight.\u201d</p>\n<p>Many of you retards took that to mean we should start infighting with republicans, celebrating the death of republicans, and dividing MAGA as much as possible.</p>\n<p>The Trump assassination attempt and Kirk assassination attempt should have united the entire right. It doesn\u2019t matter if you\u2019re a Lolbertarian, a MAGA populist, or an old blood neocon. We all have far more in common with each other than we do when the leftist commies trying to destroy America.</p>\n<p>All it took to get many of you to turn on Trump was a little bit of low IQ propaganda. Some bullshit catering to your retardation about a global pedophile ring run by Israel that Trump was protecting, because reasons. This is the opposite of the \u201cfighting\u201d that Trump was advocating.</p>\n<p>Lindsay Graham, despite his flaws, understood how to play as a team. He was once asked, \u201cwhy are you campaigning for Blake Masters when he has called you a bloodthirsty neocon for supporting the Ukraine war?\u201d</p>\n<p>His response was, \u201clook, Masters is wrong about Ukraine, but he\u2019s a Republican and I will always fight to save the senate from Democrats.\u201d</p>\n<p>This is the type of maturity and focus our movement needs to ever make an impact. Infighting because a Republican disagrees with you on 5% of issues is retarded. We all agree Islamists are the enemy and the left is the enemy. We mostly just have different opinions on how and when we should use our military.</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t support war with Russia, but these aren\u2019t disagreements worth burning the house down over. Either get on the MAGA train or get the fuck off. Trump is the leader, he supports war with Iran, as he has since the 1980s. He supports Ukraine to some mild extent.  If this is a dealbreaker for you, fine. Fuck off.</p>\n<p>If you still support Trump even though you disagree sometimes, that is fine. What is not acceptable is accusing the President of being an \u201cIsraeli shill.\u201d What is not acceptable is trying to sabotage the GOP in elections because of sloppy \u201cIsrael\u201d propaganda, like Nick Fuentes. You want to make MAGA something it never stood for and pretend you are \u201creal MAGA\u201d. Fuck off and find a new movement, you brigading faggot.</p>\n<p>The GOP is the only way to stop the left. Even if you hated Graham, you can learn something from his example of being a team player. Either follow our leader or fuck off. Uniting requires excising cancerous dividers from the movement who advocate we abandon Trump (or anyone in the GOP) because of one issue.</p>\n<p>Unite the right. Fight the left.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 17, "score_up": 19, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2076417700407173481", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqfEJfN", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 737, "suggest